Package com.teamone.unitask.timeslots

Class TimeSlotService

java.lang.Object
com.teamone.unitask.timeslots.TimeSlotService
@Service public class TimeSlotService extends Object
Service class for managing time slots within a project context. It handles operations like creating, retrieving, deleting, and finding common time slots.
